android.permission.POST_NOTIFICATIONS.info: allows an app to post notifications.
android.permission.POST_NOTIFICATIONS.description: Allows an app to post notifications

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM.info: permits exact alarm scheduling for background work.
android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM.description: Allows an app to use exact alarm scheduling APIs to perform timing sensitive background work.

android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM.info: allows using exact alarms without user permission.
android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM.description: Allows apps to use exact alarms just like with SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM but without needing to request this permission from the user. This is only intended for use by apps that rely on exact alarms for their core functionality. You should continue using SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM if your app needs exact alarms for a secondary feature that users may or may not use within your app.  Keep in mind that this is a powerful permission and app stores may enforce policies to audit and review the use of this permission. Such audits may involve removal from the app store if the app is found to be misusing this permission.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.android.vending.BILLING.description: Allows an application to make in-app purchases from Google Play.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_ME.info: enables foreground services for media playback.
android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_ME.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground with the type "mediaPlayback".

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTER.description: Permission an application must hold in order to use Settings.ACTION_REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTERY_OPTIMIZATIONS.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.READ_MEDIA_IMAGES.info: allows reading image files from external storage.
android.permission.READ_MEDIA_IMAGES.description: Allows an application to read image files from external storage.

android.permission.READ_MEDIA_VIDEO.info: allows reading video files from external storage.
android.permission.READ_MEDIA_VIDEO.description: Allows an application to read video files from external storage.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Allows an application to receive push notifications from cloud.

com.google.android.finsky.permission.BIN.description: A custom permission defined by Google.

android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_AD_.info: allow app to access the device's advertising ID.
android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_AD_.description: This ID is a unique, user-resettable identifier provided by Google's advertising services, allowing apps to track user behavior for advertising purposes while maintaining user privacy.

android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_ATT.info: allow applications to access advertising service attribution
android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_ATT.description: This enables the app to retrieve information related to advertising attribution, which can be used for targeted advertising purposes. App can gather data about how users interact with ads, such as clicks or impressions, to measure the effectiveness of advertising campaigns.

android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_TOP.info: allow applications to access advertising service topics
android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_TOP.description: This enables the app to retrieve information related to advertising topics or interests, which can be used for targeted advertising purposes.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.info: enables regular apps to use Service.startForeground.
android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground.

playstore_details.title: Yoga for Kids & Family fitness
playstore_details.description:
Yoga Kids Workouts is the best yoga training app for beginners and kids of all ages. It features a variety of yoga poses that are specially designed for kids, with fun animal names and animations. You can choose from different levels of difficulty, from easy to hard, and follow the voice instructions and timer to practice each pose correctly.

Yoga Kids Workouts is more than just an app, it’s a lifestyle. By doing yoga regularly, you and your kids will enjoy the following benefits:

Keep your cool: Yoga helps you calm your mind and manage your emotions, especially when you feel stressed, angry, or anxious.
Improve your energy: Yoga boosts your blood circulation and oxygen flow, giving you more vitality and alertness throughout the day.
Strengthen your back and posture: Yoga improves your spine alignment and core muscles, preventing back pain and injuries.
Boost your confidence: Yoga enhances your self-esteem and body image, making you feel more positive and proud of yourself.
Increase your flexibility: Yoga stretches your muscles and joints, improving your range of motion and balance.
Sleep better: Yoga relaxes your nervous system and promotes a deeper and more restful sleep.
Tone your body: Yoga burns calories and fat, shaping your body and helping you lose weight.
Have great legs: Yoga works your lower body muscles, toning your legs and glutes.
Stay fit and healthy: Yoga improves your immune system and overall health, preventing diseases and keeping you in good shape.
Have fun and bond: Yoga is a fun and enjoyable activity that you can do with your kids, creating memories and strengthening your relationship.
Yoga Kids Workouts also has nutrition facts and healthy recipes for kids, to help them learn about the importance of eating well and staying hydrated. You can also track your progress and achievements with the app, and share your results with your friends and family.

Yoga Kids Workouts is the best home workout app for kids and beginners on Google Play. You don’t need any equipment or experience, just a yoga mat and a positive attitude. Download it now and start your yoga journey with your kids today!

Whether you want to do yoga for fitness, for relaxation, or for fun, Yoga Kids Workouts has something for everyone. You can choose from different yoga games, such as Animal Yoga, where you can imitate the poses of different animals, or Yoga Challenge, where you can compete with your friends or family to see who can do the most poses. You can also customize your own yoga workout, by selecting the poses that you want to do, the duration, and the music.

Yoga Kids Workouts is the ultimate yoga app for kids and beginners. It is easy to use, interactive, and educational. It will help you and your kids develop healthy habits, improve your focus, and boost your confidence. It will also make you and your kids happy, as you will have fun and bond while doing something good for your body and mind.

Yoga Kids Workouts is the perfect app for anyone who wants to start doing yoga, or for anyone who wants to do yoga with their kids. It is suitable for all ages and levels, from toddlers to teens, from beginners to advanced. It is also free to download and use, so you have nothing to lose and everything to gain.

What are you waiting for? Download Yoga Kids Workouts today and discover the amazing benefits of yoga for yourself and your kids!
